318→   318→   318→    // happens at the WebSocket protocol layer, not HTTP middleware.
319→   319→   319→    // A plain GET returns 400 (not a WebSocket upgrade), but crucially
320→   320→   320→    // it must NOT return a 303 redirect to /login.
